column35: Health experts want deeper probe of FDA donations – The Manila Times
column36: A group of public health experts have asked authorities to conduct deeper investigation of the alleged donation by Bloomberg Philanthropies to the Philippine Food and Drug Administration (FDA) to see if it has violated any law in the Philippines and the United States.
